title: Insta-Lizard Contest
description:
How To Win The Passion
1. Follow @suprafootwear on instagram.
2. Tag your photos #thepassion so Lizard can pick his favorite instagrams.
3. Visit instalizard.com to see your photos and find out if you've won The Passion!

*Contest ended last November 2012. Thanks to everyone who entered. Keep hash tagging #thepassion 

SITE: http://www.suprafootwear.com
